title: BIP to Create new token to farm with $BLOODY LP's
body:
This is a Bloody Improvment Proposal to Create a new token that can be farmed with $BLOODY LP's on Bloodyfi.org

The new token will be a low supply cap, deflationary, burn token (similar to $nice and $nice tokenomics). 

Burn 1% up to supply 100 
Rebase Burn to 12.5% at supply 100 until supply is down to 1.
Then return 1% burn until supply is back to 100.

New token name options: Clot, Vessel, Heart, Vase, Flask. etc. to be chosen by "TIm" or voted on if this prop passes.
choices: Maybe, but I want to her what Tim thinks
